            throws IllegalMoveException
Inserts a node under a specific parent in the tree structure.In order to eliminate confusion we follow these steps: 1.Move the pointer to subparent 2.Access subparent's child array and find the parent. 3.move the pointer to the parent. 4.insert a new node pointing to the parent. !!! use subParent name null in case of intending insertion at root.
